ersity of Wisconsin-Madison Graduate\nSchool, and is now publicly available on the WIYN Telescope through the\nNational Optical Astronomical Observatories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2004 20:13:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
