ulation of X-ray\nsources which have optical properties of Type 1 (unobscured) quasars, but X-ray\nproperties of Type 2 (obscured) quasars. We show that the observed distribution\nof optical-to-X-ray flux ratios of quasars at z>1 is skewed to low values\ncompared to the intrinsic distribution...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2004 22:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
